<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-HK">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="color-scheme" content="light dark">
  <meta name="description" content="本平台提供台灣一番賞代購、代抽、代收與跨境轉送服務，所有抽選行為於台灣完成，香港地區僅提供商品領取與寄送。">
  <title><%= raffle.title %> - 台灣一番賞委託代抽</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/" class="site-logo">
        <img src="/img/mirai-3.png" alt="TMA台灣分部-未來飛翔">
      </a>
      <a href="/" class="back-link">← 返回首頁</a>
      <% if (raffle.cover_image) { %>
        <img class="raffle-header-cover" src="<%= raffle.cover_image %>" width="1200" height="240" alt="<%= raffle.title %> 封面">
      <% } %>
      <h1><%= raffle.title %></h1>
      <p><%= raffle.description %></p>
      <div class="raffle-header-stats">
        <span class="stat-badge">
          <strong>剩餘</strong>: <%= remainingCount %> / <%= raffle.total_boxes %>
        </span>
        <span class="stat-badge price">
          <strong>價格</strong>: HK$<%= formatMoney(raffle.price_per_box) %> / NT$<%= formatMoney(raffle.price_per_box * twdPerHkd, 0) %>
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="container">
    <% if (remainingCount <= 0) { %>
      <div class="alert warning">
        <strong>此代抽服務已完結</strong>，所有項目已被預定。
      </div>
    <% } %>

    <!-- Entry Form -->
    <% if (remainingCount > 0 && raffle.status === 'active') { %>
      <section class="entry-section">
        <h2>委託代抽</h2>

        <div class="legal-notice" style="background: #e7f3ff; border: 1px solid #b6d4fe; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
          <p style="margin: 0; color: #084298; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;">
            <strong>付款說明：</strong>付款即委託本站參與台灣一番賞抽選，費用含代抽、物流及處理成本。抽選結果依台灣官方公佈，本站不干涉結果。
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="payment-alert">
          <p>🔒 <strong>需要驗證碼才能委託代抽</strong></p>
          <p>請先付款給管理員，獲得驗證碼後輸入下方完成委託</p>
          <div style="margin-top: 12px;">
            <a class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm" target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://wa.me/85295713359?text=我要預約一番賞代抽">香港客服</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm" target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://wa.me/85295713359?text=我要預約一番賞代抽">台灣客服</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
          <label style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; cursor: pointer;">
            <input type="checkbox" id="batchModeToggle">
            <span>啟用批量代抽模式（一次輸入多個驗證碼）</span>
          </label>
        </div>

        <!-- Age Verification Checkbox -->
        <div style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 12px; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 6px;">
          <label style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px; cursor: pointer;">
            <input type="checkbox" id="ageConfirmation" required style="margin-top: 3px;">
            <span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;">我確認本人已年滿18歲，並了解本服務僅為台灣一番賞代抽委託，所有抽選行為均於台灣完成</span>
          </label>
        </div>

        <!-- Single Mode -->
        <form id="drawForm" class="draw-form">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="verification_code">驗證碼</label>
            <input type="text" id="verification_code" name="verification_code" autocomplete="one-time-code" required placeholder="請輸入管理員給你的驗證碼">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="username">會員用戶名</label>
            <input type="text" id="username" name="username" required placeholder="請輸入你的會員用戶名" value="<%= currentUser ? currentUser.username : '' %>" <%= currentUser ? 'readonly' : '' %>>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="contact">聯絡方式</label>
            <input type="text" id="contact" name="contact" required placeholder="請輸入電話或WhatsApp">
          </div>
          <button type="submit" id="drawBtn" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">確認驗證碼，提交委託!</button>
        </form>

        <!-- Batch Mode -->
        <form id="batchDrawForm" class="draw-form" style="display: none;">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="batch_codes">驗證碼列表 <small>（每行一個 或者 用逗號分隔都得）</small></label>
            <textarea id="batch_codes" name="batch_codes" rows="8" required placeholder="請貼上你的驗證碼，支援兩種格式:&#10;每行一個: AAA-BBB-CCC&#10;            DDD-EEE-FFF&#10;&#10;或者逗號分隔: AAA-BBB-CCC, DDD-EEE-FFF, GGG-HHH-III"></textarea>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="batch_username">會員用戶名</label>
            <input type="text" id="batch_username" name="batch_username" required placeholder="所有代抽都會用呢個用戶名" value="<%= currentUser ? currentUser.username : '' %>" <%= currentUser ? 'readonly' : '' %>>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="batch_contact">聯絡方式</label>
            <input type="text" id="batch_contact" name="batch_contact" required placeholder="所有代抽都會用呢個聯絡方式">
          </div>
          <button type="submit" id="batchDrawBtn" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">開始批量委託 (<span id="batchCount">0</span> 個)</button>
        </form>
      </section>

      <!-- Result Modal -->
      <div id="resultModal" class="modal hidden">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <h2>抽選結果</h2>
          <div id="resultContent" class="result-content">
            <!-- Filled by JS -->
          </div>
          <button id="closeResult" class="btn btn-secondary">關閉</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Batch Results Area -->
      <div id="batchResultsArea" class="entry-section" style="margin-top: 24px; display: none;">
        <h3>批量抽選結果</h3>
        <div id="batchResultsContent" style="max-height: 500px; overflow-y: auto; margin-top: 12px;">
          <!-- Filled by JS -->
        </div>
      </div>
    <% } %>

    <!-- Item List by Pool -->
    <section class="item-section">
      <h2>商品內容一覽</h2>
      <div style="background: #f0f9ff; border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9; padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <p style="margin: 0; color: #0c4a6e; font-size: 14px;">
          <strong>最終賞（LAST賞）說明：</strong>購買整盒最後一個商品就會獲得最終賞，最終賞隨整盒附送。
        </p>
      </div>
      <% pools.forEach(pool => { %>
        <% if (pools.length > 1) { %>
          <h3 class="pool-title">第 <%= pool.number %> 商品池</h3>
        <% } %>
        <div class="prize-list">
          <% pool.prizes.forEach(prize => { %>
            <div class="prize-card <%= prize.is_final ? 'final-prize' : '' %> <%= prize.remaining_count <= 0 ? 'sold-out' : '' %>">
              <div class="prize-header">
                <span class="tier-badge <%= prize.tier.toLowerCase() %>"><%= prize.tier %></span>
                <% if (prize.is_final) { %>
                  <span class="final-badge">最終賞</span>
                <% } %>
                <span class="count-badge">
                  <%= prize.remaining_count %> / <%= prize.total_count %>
                </span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="prize-name"><%= prize.name %></h3>
              <% if (prize.description) { %>
                <p class="prize-description"><%= prize.description %></p>
              <% } %>
              <% if (prize.remaining_count <= 0) { %>
                <div class="sold-out-overlay">已預定</div>
              <% } %>
            </div>
          <% }) %>
        </div>
      <% }) %>
    </section>

    <!-- Result List -->
    <section class="result-section">
      <h2>抽選結果記錄</h2>
      <% if (winners.length === 0) { %>
        <div class="empty-state">
          <p>暫無抽選結果記錄</p>
        </div>
      <% } else { %>
        <div style="background: var(--card-bg); border-radius: var(--border-radius); overflow: hidden; box-shadow: var(--shadow); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);">
          <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
            <tbody>
              <% winners.forEach(winner => { %>
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 10px 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); width: 18%;"><%= winner.buyer_name %></td>
                  <td style="padding: 10px 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><%= winner.prize_name %></td>
                  <td style="padding: 10px 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); width: 30%; color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem;"><%= new Date(winner.drawn_at).toLocaleString('zh-TW', { timeZone: 'Asia/Taipei' }) %></td>
                </tr>
              <% }) %>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      <% } %>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal-footer" style="background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; color: #495057;">
        <strong>【服務聲明】</strong><br>
        <ol style="margin: 8px 0 0 20px; padding: 0;">
          <li>本平台僅提供日本／台灣一番賞商品之代購及代抽服務。</li>
          <li>所有抽選行為及相關交易均於海外（台灣）由當地合作單位完成，香港僅作為資訊展示及代購安排之平台，不涉及任何抽獎、博彩或機會遊戲活動之經營或操作。</li>
          <li>由於相關抽選活動並非於香港進行，本平台並不構成香港法例下之獎券、抽獎或賭博業務。</li>
          <li>用戶於下單時，即表示已年滿18歲，明白及同意抽選行為於海外進行，接受抽選結果之隨機性及不可預測性。</li>
          <li>所有商品內容、款式及中獎機率，均以當地官方公佈為準。基於抽選性質，所有訂單一經確認恕不接受退款或更換。</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Ichiban Kuji Proxy Service</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 8px; opacity: 0.7;">Powered by TMA台灣分部-未來飛翔</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <input type="hidden" id="raffleId" value="<%= raffle.id %>">

  <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
  <script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
      const raffleId = parseInt(document.getElementById('raffleId').value, 10);
      initRafflePage(raffleId);

      // Age confirmation check before submit
      const ageCheck = document.getElementById('ageConfirmation');
      const forms = [document.getElementById('drawForm'), document.getElementById('batchDrawForm')];
      forms.forEach(form => {
        form.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
          if (!ageCheck.checked) {
            e.preventDefault();
            alert('必須確認已年滿18歲才能使用本服務');
            return false;
          }
        });
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
